name: GDB Natural Dog Muffins
description:
These organic dog muffins will be  a great for a snack between meals or as a training reward for your canine friend. Baked fresh to order and contains no dairy or egg products. All our dog muffins are organic  and homemade with no added artificial colors, flavors, preservatives, salt or sugar. 

Dog muffins are packaged in environmental friendly biodegradable recyclable paper bags.  Each bag contains 18 muffins. 

Percentage of proceeds for each sale will be donated to the efforts support the Atlanta Humane Society. 

Organics Ingredients:
Blue Cornmeal, Rye Flour, Spinach, Carrots, Celery

Guaranteed Analysis: 
Crude Protein (Min)        6% 
Crude Fat (Min)              0.5% 
Crude Fiber (Max)          2% 
Moisture (Max)               56%
